title: VirtuSwap_official
author: VirtuSwap_official
content: VirtuSwap is a DEX with lower trading costs and higher LP returns using reserve-pool-based technology and financial engineering.The idea of the project is also to educate crypto users about hidden taxes and the solution VirtuSwap is providing to reduce them. There's a nice video with explanation of the technology: https://youtu.be/tnmI3HjORqsVirtuSwap is moving closer to the Testnet launch, stay tuned...You can learn more on our website: http://virtuswap.ioMedium http://medium.com/virtuswapBoth of our audits(https://github.com/Virtuswap/v1-core/blob/main/audits/REP-final-20220915T000103Z.pdf)(https://github.com/Virtuswap/v1-core/blob/main/audits/VirtuSwap_Security_Analysis_by_Pessimistic.pdf)Join Twitter https://twitter.com/VirtuSwapJoin Telegram https://t.me/official_virtuswapTo raise awareness and help generate usage, we will be running several incentivization (airdrop) programs over the course of the coming weeks. Don't miss!
